# Design tokens — Arabic-friendly defaults

> Drop these into Figma Variables, Tailwind config, Style Dictionary, or
> your design-system layer. The goal: every new Arabic surface inherits
> shaping-aware defaults without designers relearning the rules.

## Font stack

```json
{
  "font.family.arabic.display":  ["Tajawal", "Noto Naskh Arabic", "Amiri", "serif"],
  "font.family.arabic.body":     ["Tajawal", "Noto Naskh Arabic", "system-ui", "sans-serif"],
  "font.family.arabic.mono":     ["Fira Code Arabic", "Vazirmatn Mono", "monospace"],
  "font.family.mixed":           ["Tajawal", "Inter", "Noto Naskh Arabic", "system-ui", "sans-serif"]
}
```

| Token | Notes |
|---|---|
| `font.size.step` | Arabic body needs ~7–10% more leading than Latin for equivalent readability. |
| `font.weight.arabic.bold` | 700 in Latin is 600 in Arabic at equivalent visual weight. |
| `line-height.arabic` | 1.7 (vs 1.5 default) — diacritics need vertical breathing room. |

## Spacing & direction

```json
{
  "direction":            "rtl",
  "logical.properties":   true,
  "letter-spacing":       0,
  "word-spacing.arabic":  "0.05em"
}
```

> **Rule**: never set `letter-spacing` on an Arabic run. Set
> `word-spacing` instead.

## Color & shape

```json
{
  "stroke.padding-inline":  "16px",
  "margin.inline.start":    "auto",     /* in RTL, "start" = right */
  "icon.mirror.inRTL":      ["arrow", "chevron", "play"]
}
```

Icons that imply direction (arrows, chevrons, progress bars) MUST
mirror in RTL — even brand logos you didn't know had directionality
(reports, signposts, time indicators).

## Numerals

```json
{
  "numeral.system":     "auto",          /* native: ٠١٢ vs Latin: 012 */
  "date.locale":        "ar-SA",
  "calendar":           "islamic-umalqura",
  "currency.fallback":  "SAR"
}
```

Decide per-product: technical UIs usually prefer Latin digits, content
UIs usually prefer Arabic-Indic. Don't mix.

## Layout

| Slot | Western (LTR) | Arabic (RTL) |
|---|---|---|
| Reading edge | left | right |
| Pagination | next = right | next = left |
| Carousel | autoplay L→R | autoplay R→L |
| Breadcrumb | Home › Section › Page | الصفحة › القسم › الرئيسية |
| Modal close | top-right | top-left |
| `align-items: start` in flex | left edge | right edge |
